dmca.title: WaySpa stressed by claimed copying
dmca.body:
1.	The copywrited work is located in the body content of the web site "Spas Word Wide" and located on the home page (www.spasworldwide.com)

2.	The Web search "wayspa Toronto" brings up spasworldwide.com on the 2nd page of results. The copy
"WaySpa offers discounts on spa packages from premium spas in Toronto - only the finest spas are featured on our site so that we can provide the highest level of service at the best prices available. Save up to 50% off the in-spa price"
Is all over their site.
